{
  "page": "Burning of the seats of the pious lords",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Burning of the seats of the pious lords</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/43_AC\" title=\"43 AC\">43&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nDestruction of the seats of several pious lords</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></b><br /></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">Rebellious noble houses:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blanetree\" title=\"House Blanetree\"><img alt=\"House Blanetree.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/86/House_Blanetree.svg/20px-House_Blanetree.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/86/House_Blanetree.svg/30px-House_Blanetree.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/86/House_Blanetree.svg/40px-House_Blanetree.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Blanetree\" title=\"House Blanetree\">House Blanetree</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Terrick\" title=\"House Terrick\"><img alt=\"House Terrick.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/House_Terrick.svg/20px-House_Terrick.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/House_Terrick.svg/30px-House_Terrick.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b7/House_Terrick.svg/40px-House_Terrick.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Terrick\" title=\"House Terrick\">House Terrick</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Deddings\" title=\"House Deddings\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Deddings\" title=\"House Deddings\">House Deddings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lychester\" title=\"House Lychester\"><img alt=\"House Lychester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e3/House_Lychester.svg/20px-House_Lychester.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e3/House_Lychester.svg/30px-House_Lychester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e3/House_Lychester.svg/40px-House_Lychester.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lychester\" title=\"House Lychester\">House Lychester</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wayn\" title=\"House Wayn\"><img alt=\"House Wayn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/56/House_Wayn.svg/20px-House_Wayn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/56/House_Wayn.svg/30px-House_Wayn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/56/House_Wayn.svg/40px-House_Wayn.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Wayn\" title=\"House Wayn\">House Wayn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Broome\" title=\"House Broome\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Broome\" title=\"House Broome\">House Broome</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Falwell\" title=\"House Falwell\"><img alt=\"House Falwell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/House_Falwell.svg/20px-House_Falwell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/House_Falwell.svg/30px-House_Falwell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3e/House_Falwell.svg/40px-House_Falwell.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Falwell\" title=\"House Falwell\">House Falwell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lorch\" title=\"House Lorch\"><img alt=\"House Lorch.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/20px-House_Lorch.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/30px-House_Lorch.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/40px-House_Lorch.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lorch\" title=\"House Lorch\">House Lorch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Doggett\" title=\"House Doggett\"><img alt=\"House Doggett.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1a/House_Doggett.svg/20px-House_Doggett.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1a/House_Doggett.svg/30px-House_Doggett.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1a/House_Doggett.svg/40px-House_Doggett.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Doggett\" title=\"House Doggett\">House Doggett</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><div class=\"plainlist\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Queen Dowager <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a></li></ul>\n</div></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <div class=\"plainlist\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blanetree\" title=\"House Blanetree\"><img alt=\"House Blanetree.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/86/House_Blanetree.svg/20px-House_Blanetree.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/86/House_Blanetree.svg/30px-House_Blanetree.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/86/House_Blanetree.svg/40px-House_Blanetree.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Blanetree</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Terrick\" title=\"House Terrick\"><img alt=\"House Terrick.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/House_Terrick.svg/20px-House_Terrick.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/House_Terrick.svg/30px-House_Terrick.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b7/House_Terrick.svg/40px-House_Terrick.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Terrick</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Deddings\" title=\"House Deddings\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Deddings</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lychester\" title=\"House Lychester\"><img alt=\"House Lychester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e3/House_Lychester.svg/20px-House_Lychester.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e3/House_Lychester.svg/30px-House_Lychester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e3/House_Lychester.svg/40px-House_Lychester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Lychester</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wayn\" title=\"House Wayn\"><img alt=\"House Wayn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/56/House_Wayn.svg/20px-House_Wayn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/56/House_Wayn.svg/30px-House_Wayn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/56/House_Wayn.svg/40px-House_Wayn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Wayn</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Broome\" title=\"House Broome\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Broome</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Falwell\" title=\"House Falwell\"><img alt=\"House Falwell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/House_Falwell.svg/20px-House_Falwell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/House_Falwell.svg/30px-House_Falwell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3e/House_Falwell.svg/40px-House_Falwell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Falwell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lorch\" title=\"House Lorch\"><img alt=\"House Lorch.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/20px-House_Lorch.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/30px-House_Lorch.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/40px-House_Lorch.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Lorch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Doggett\" title=\"House Doggett\"><img alt=\"House Doggett.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1a/House_Doggett.svg/20px-House_Doggett.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1a/House_Doggett.svg/30px-House_Doggett.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1a/House_Doggett.svg/40px-House_Doggett.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Doggett</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">2 dragons:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Castle garrisons</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">None</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Massive\n<ul><li>Lord Doggett</li>\n<li>Lady Doggett</li>\n<li>Daughter of Lord Doggett</li>\n<li>Lord Doggett's sworn swords</li>\n<li>Lord Doggett's serving men</li></ul></td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Late in the year <a href=\"/index.php/43_AC\" title=\"43 AC\">43&#160;AC</a>, in response to the defiance of several noble houses, both Queen Dowager <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> and King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> carried out a series of <b>burnings</b> of the seats of several \"pious lords\" that defiant to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Burnings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Burnings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Burning_of_the_seats_of_the_pious_lords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the wake of the victory of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Great_Fork\" title=\"Battle at the Great Fork\">Battle at the Great Fork</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> remained defiant against the crown. The <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aenys_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Aenys I)\">High Septon</a> made denunciations both against Maegor and his wives as \"the abomination and his whores\" as well as the daughters of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_the_Uncrowned\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Aegon the Uncrowned\">Aegon the Uncrowned</a>, regarded as abominations and fruits of lust and <a href=\"/index.php/Incest\" title=\"Incest\">incest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>For their part, the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a> remained active. Thousands of <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a> haunted roads and remote locations in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>, as well as the lands surrounding the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">Trident</a>, in small bands that fell upon travelers and swarmed towns, villages and poorly defended castles, killing whatever king's loyalists they came upon. With Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Horys_Hill\" title=\"Horys Hill\">Horys Hill</a> lost much of his support after Faith Militant's defeat at the Great Fork, new leaders arose among the Poor Fellows, such as <a href=\"/index.php/Ragged_Silas\" title=\"Ragged Silas\">Ragged Silas</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Septon_Moon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Septon Moon\">Septon Moon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Dennis_the_Lame\" title=\"Dennis the Lame\">Dennis the Lame</a>. Meanwhile, the <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a> elected Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Doggett\" title=\"Joffrey Doggett\">Joffrey Doggett</a> as their new <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_captain\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grand captain\">grand captain</a>. Ser Joffrey and a hundred men set out from their chapterhouse in <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> to seek the blessing of the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a>. By the time the Warrior's Sons arrived at <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, their numbers rose to two thousand, among <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squires</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Freerider\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Freerider\">freeriders</a>. Elsewhere, lords and followers of the Faith gathered men and plotted ways to bring down the crown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The crown was aware of these events, and <a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">ravens</a> were sent to summon lords and <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a> suspected of disloyalty to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to bend the knee, do homage to the king and present a son or daughter as <a href=\"/index.php/Hostage\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hostage\">hostage</a>. The Faith Militant, for their part, were <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaw\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Outlaw\">outlawed</a>, with <a href=\"/index.php/King_Maegor%27s_laws\" title=\"King Maegor&#39;s laws\">membership declared punishable by death</a>, and the High Septon was commanded to deliver himself to the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> to stand trial under charges of high treason. The High Septon's response was a summon to the king, commanding him to present himself to the <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a> to beg the forgiveness of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven-Faced_God\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Seven-Faced God\">gods</a> for his sins and cruelties. And while some of the pious lords summoned to the capital obeyed the king and presented themselves to do homage and deliver hostages, the majority refused and remained at their seats.\n</p><p>King Maegor, however, was devoted to the completion of the Red Keep. He remained inactive for almost half a year.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Burnings\">Burnings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Burning_of_the_seats_of_the_pious_lords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Burnings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>With Maegor busy with the construction of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>, Dowager Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> took wing upon <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a> and flew to the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> and set aflame the seats of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blanetree\" title=\"House Blanetree\">House Blanetree</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Terrick\" title=\"House Terrick\">House Terrick</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Deddings\" title=\"House Deddings\">House Deddings</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lychester\" title=\"House Lychester\">House Lychester</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wayn\" title=\"House Wayn\">House Wayn</a>, all in a single night.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Afterwards, Maegor, mounted <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a> the Black Dread, and flew to the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>, where he burned the seats of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Broome\" title=\"House Broome\">House Broome</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Falwell\" title=\"House Falwell\">House Falwell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lorch\" title=\"House Lorch\">House Lorch</a> and, finally, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Doggett\" title=\"House Doggett\">House Doggett</a>, which was reduced to ashes, and claiming the lives of the parents and younger sister of Ser Joffrey Doggett, as well as their entire household.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Burning_of_the_seats_of_the_pious_lords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the destruction of the seats of the defiant lords, Maegor and Visenya <a href=\"/index.php/Submission_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Submission of Oldtown\">set their sights</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> and flew south.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Burning_of_the_seats_of_the_pious_lords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Template:Faith Militant uprising\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Faith_Militant_upr